Package menu

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FarmingMenu
    The FarmingMenu class represents the menu class for function "Plant", "Harvest" and "Clear".
    FriendMenu
    The FriendMenu class represents the menu class for function "Accept", "Unfriend", "Request" and "Reject".
    InventoryMenu
    The InventoryMenu class represents the menu class for function "Buy Seed" and "Send Gift".
    LoginMenu
    The LoginMenu class represents the menu class for function "Log In".
    MainMenu
    The MainMenu class represents the menu class for the default menu shown when users login with correct username and password.
    RegisterMenu
    The RegisterMenu class represents the menu class for function "Register".
    WelcomePage
    The WelcomeMenu class represents the menu class for the default menu shown when the application is started.
